This is a trend‑aligned SPX scalping strategy designed for fast day trades on 1–5 minute charts. It enters on pullbacks within a strong EMA trend, confirmed by RSI momentum and above‑average volume, and exits quickly using ATR‑based stops, targets, optional trailing stops, and a time‑based exit to avoid overstaying trades.
